            "body": "> What decorations and lua callbacks? Please link to their source code.\r\n\r\nThese two files define the Snacks terminal\r\n* https://github.com/folke/snacks.nvim/blob/a049339328e2599ad6e85a69fa034ac501e921b2/lua/snacks/terminal.lua\r\n* https://github.com/folke/snacks.nvim/blob/a049339328e2599ad6e85a69fa034ac501e921b2/lua/snacks/win.lua\r\n\r\nI couldn't narrow down the issue to single cause in this lua code, but the [winbar](https://github.com/folke/snacks.nvim/blob/a049339328e2599ad6e85a69fa034ac501e921b2/lua/snacks/terminal.lua#L95-L96) and other lua overhead might be adding some latency.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nYes, your new PR appears to have fixed it.",
